  +mupen64-0.5-r3.ebuild:
  New revision with better support for multilib installs.

  22 Feb 2007; Simon Stelling <blubb@gentoo.org> mupen64-0.5-r2.ebuild:
  depend on >=emul-sdl-10.0; bug 167202

